snippet.title: Jason Momoa BEGS Aquaman 2 Director to Fire Amber Heard
snippet.description:
►Jason Momoa BEGS Aquaman 2 Director to Fire Amber Heard
The topic of a sequel was brought up for discussion in 2018. James Wan will also serve as the director of his film. It has been confirmed that Jason and Yahya Abdul-Mateen II will reprise their roles as Aquaman and Black Manta in the upcoming film. The film will be released on December 16, 2022, according to the official release date.
